high_descs: wash and remove tomato from sink
Turn around, walk to the island in the middle of the room
Pick up the tomato from the island
Turn around, walk to the sink
Set the tomato in the sink, rinse with water, remove the tomato from the sink
Turn around, walk to the fridge on the left
Open the fridge, set the tomato inside, close the door
Turn around and go to the kitchen island.
Pick up the tomato nearest to you on the kitchen island.
Turn around and go to the sink in the middle of the counter.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it, then turn the water off and pick the tomato back up.
Turn around and face the refrigerator .
Open the refrigerator and put the rinsed tomato inside.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the tomato from the kitchen island and put it in the refrigerator.
